trans-unit.source: Instances of this class are passed to the <xref:System.Net.UploadDataCompletedEventHandler>.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別的執行個體傳遞至<xref:System.Net.UploadDataCompletedEventHandler>。

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates asynchronously uploading data.
trans-unit.target: 下列程式碼範例示範如何以非同步方式上載資料。

trans-unit.source: The following method is called when the upload completes.
trans-unit.target: 上傳完成時，會呼叫下列方法。

trans-unit.source: Gets the server reply to a data upload operation started by calling an <see cref="Overload:System.Net.WebClient.UploadDataAsync" /> method.
trans-unit.target: 取得伺服器對資料上載作業 (呼叫 <see cref="Overload:System.Net.WebClient.UploadDataAsync" /> 方法所啟動) 的回應。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Byte" /> array containing the server reply.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Byte" /> 陣列，包含伺服器回應。

trans-unit.source: You should check the <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A> and <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Cancelled%2A> properties before using the data returned by this property.
trans-unit.target: 您應該檢查<xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A>和<xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Cancelled%2A>的屬性，才能使用這個屬性所傳回的資料。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A> property's value is an <xref:System.Exception> object or the <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Cancelled%2A> property's value is `true`, the asynchronous operation did not complete correctly and the <xref:System.Net.UploadDataCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> property's value will not be valid.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A>屬性的值是<xref:System.Exception>物件或<xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Cancelled%2A>屬性的值是`true`，非同步作業未正確完成和<xref:System.Net.UploadDataCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A>屬性的值將不再有效。

trans-unit.source: The following code example displays the value of this property.
trans-unit.target: 下列程式碼範例會顯示這個屬性的值。
